text.tspan: The Facility Management feature simplifies routine maintenance and administrative work by
enabling the easy creation of to-do lists and the digital recording of all work activities. This
module allows staff to track assignments, update progress in real-time, and generate accurate
work reports directly within the system. By centralizing task management and documentation, it
ensures efficiency, clear accountability, and provides management with auditable records of all
The purpose of the Document Sharing feature is to
facilitate and expedite the process for employees to
find supporting documents that serve as essential
reference materials. By centralizing the document
repository and enabling easy sharing, this feature
significantly reduces search time and ensures all
personnel have immediate access to the correct,
standardized documentation needed for their tasks.
